thread.title: BRIEF-IGD SIIQ FY Net Profit Up At EUR 86.5 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-IGD SIIQ FY Net Profit Up At EUR 86.5 Mln
text:
Feb 22 (Reuters) - IMMOBILIARE GRANDE DISTRIBUZIONE SIIQ SPA:
* FY NET PROFIT EUR 86.5 MILLION VERSUS EUR 68.3 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY CORE BUSINESS REVENUE EUR 145.1 MILLION, UP 6.0 PERCENT YEAR ON YEAR
* PROPOSES DIVIDEND OF AROUND EUROCENTS 50-52 PER SHARE, UPON DEFINITION OF FINAL TERMS OF CAPITAL INCREASE
* ESTIMATES GROWTH IN FFO IN RANGE OF BETWEEN +18% TO +20% IN 2018 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
